{"tid":971022,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"放過摩連奴啦！路人竟然咁挑佢機","createTime":"2019-01-06T10:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T17:44:17.000Z","uid":54870,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1527af1f5e9e960812735d81ba2b0a2f9a8ed401","tid":971022,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:24:32.000Z","msg":"曼聯喺英足盃第3圈主場以2:0砌低雷丁，解僱摩連奴後復活5連勝，相信寸王個心總有啲唔自在，點知英國狗仔隊仲發現，佢喺倫敦屋企嘅門口外畀路人挑佢機，認真慘情！<br />\n<br />\n據講摩連奴出門後遇到個球迷，對方好熱心咁，畀咗啲戰術同排陣嘅建議佢，或者覺得個大叔冇咩敵意，寸王都幾耐心咁聽，期間仲有同人揸下手，接受完指導後就露出謎之微笑離開，全程冇發脾氣。不過咁，摩連奴始終係最出色教頭之一，要佢小學雞咁聽個路人指導，都真係有啲不受尊重，希望呢個大叔放過佢，唔好再咁搞啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLGdi4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLGdi4r.jpg&h=dc21252f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb6ecd80886b03d2b0ba67e0a053e6d509b10588","tid":971022,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:27:31.000Z","msg":"仲留係英國把撚咩<br />\n咩葡萄牙啦"},{"pid":"88a5e0fb0c73dc39c2fa1b42befa743a1f0c8858","tid":971022,"uid":87394,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"真迷摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d3de2f4bc6f23a6870512020f5bf93fdd052ea","tid":971022,"uid":19029,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:28:25.000Z","msg":"違約金殺手"},{"pid":"b29aa43b405d40216d85723f8893033500cfdb23","tid":971022,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eca219deca584c6cb43be951db68bec871f09fb","tid":971022,"uid":41524,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"做得獌狗遇咗要還"},{"pid":"36d78fe2211249d63fc1fddb874487deadf9a711","tid":971022,"uid":29080,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"何蛇嚟"},{"pid":"a4c94c22db24ae77675c8fbf3f6c3975786b643a","tid":971022,"uid":77355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedB